tasks/restart_profile.yml (UPDATED)

✅ No ternary for ps discovery or start
✅ Uses ps_discover_one.yml and start_one_jvm.yml
✅ Uses restart_started_jvm.yml (already split)
✅ Uses record_one_jvm.yml to avoid loop-over-block
